comments: Melton (MEM) and James (LAL) make incidental contact with one another as they each attempt to gain control of the loose ball.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: James (LAL) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Bazemore (LAL) brushes Morant's (MEM) left arm/side and marginal contact occurs at the end of Morant's drive.
Bazemore's (LAL) arms extend forward as he braces for the impending contact with Jackson Jr. (MEM) during the drive and the contact is marginal.
Bazemore (LAL) initiates contact across Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) left arm and causes Jackson Jr. to lose control of the ball after his gather.
Bane (MEM) engages and disengages with James (LAL) near the elbow.
Adams (MEM) and Westbrook (LAL) engage and disengage with one another as the screen is set.
Davis (LAL) re-establishes slightly in Bane's (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs to Bane's upper half as Davis sets the pick.
James (LAL) extends his right leg and marginal contact occurs with Bane's (MEM) leg during the follow-through of James' jump shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) brushes Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) side and marginal body contact occurs as Jackson Jr. retrieves the rebound.
Bazemore (LAL) extends his right forearm forward and incidental contact occurs with Bane's (MEM) head/neck area after his gather.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Morant's (MEM) view and gives Morant a step of distance to avoid the contact, which Davis absorbs.
Adams (MEM) cleanly blocks Westbrook's (LAL) shot attempt near the rim.
Anthony (LAL) and Melton (MEM) come together at the same spot in the lane and marginal contact occurs to Melton's upper half as Anthony releases away to retrieve the rebound.
Melton (MEM) brushes Anthony's (LAL) left arm and marginal contact occurs during the layup attempt.
Adams (MEM) and Anthony (LAL) engage and disengage with one another in the lane.
Adams (MEM) is deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Replay review of the foul called on Anthony (LAL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Anthony dislodges the ball away from Morant (MEM) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Adams (MEM) engages and disengages with Davis (LAL) as Davis moves to defend the shot.
Davis (LAL) jumps along Morant's (MEM) path to the basket and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Westbrook (LAL) moves over the screen and marginal contact occurs with Melton's (MEM) upper half during the inbound.
Bazemore (LAL) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Adams (MEM) extends outward as he firms up in his screening position and some contact occurs with Anthony's (LAL) upper half as Anthony attempts to get over. The contact is marginal.
Westbrook (LAL) and Melton (MEM) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.

Replay review of the foul called on Adams (MEM) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Adams retreats away from Davis (LAL) before Davis falls to the floor on his own after stealing the inbound. The game clock was reset to 0:49.0 after review.
Morant's (MEM) right foot lands out of bounds while he still maintains possession of the ball.
Adams (MEM) moves into Bazemore's (LAL) space and marginal body contact occurs after Bazemore steals the ball.
Bane (MEM) delivers contact to James' (LAL) back after James receives the pass.
Anthony (LAL) and Melton (MEM) engage and disengage with one another off-ball. Upon disengaging, Anthony grasps and then quickly releases Melton's jersey as he receives the entry pass.
Melton (MEM) legally contests Anthony's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Adams (MEM) makes clean with the ball and dislodges it away from Westbrook (LAL) before he or Jackson Jr. make any incidental contact with Westbrook thereafter.
The ball touches Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) right hand and then is saved prior to making contact with the baseline.
Bazemore (LAL) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
Morant (MEM) commits a take foul on Monk (LAL).
Davis (LAL) commits a take foul on Jackson Jr. (MEM).
Jackson Jr. (MEM) extends his arm outward and initiates contact with Davis' (LAL) upper half and side, affecting his SQBR during the inbound.
Davis (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Morant's (MEM) path and does not deliver the contact.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) commits a take foul on Davis (LAL).
Bazemore (LAL) initiates contact with Morant's (MEM) right arm during his upward shooting motion and affects his jump shot attempt.
Adams (MEM) and Davis (LAL) grasp each other's arm during rebounding and marginal contact occurs as the rebound falls overhead.
Adams (MEM) commits a take foul on Anthony (LAL). After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined the foul occurred with 1.9 seconds remaining in the quarter.
Westbrook (LAL) cleanly steals the inbound pass intended for Bane (MEM). After conferencing, the crew determined an inadvertent whistle was blown with 0.3 seconds remaining in the quarter.
